<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Question and Answer on Your Video</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .content {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>New Activity on Your Video</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Someone has asked a question on your video titled "<%= title %>", and an answer has been provided.</p>
            <p>You can view the discussion and participate further by visiting your video.</p>
            <p>Thank you for being an active member of our community!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Our Service. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
